Class GlobalFullCompactionSinkWrite

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.sink.StoreSinkWriteImpl
      • org.apache.paimon.flink.sink.GlobalFullCompactionSinkWrite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StoreSinkWrite

    public class GlobalFullCompactionSinkWrite
extends StoreSinkWriteImpl
    StoreSinkWrite for execute full compaction globally. All writers will be full compaction at the same time (in the specified checkpoint).
